	(62,12,'audition_blurb','Please read all the details on the audition information sheet, and fill in the <a href=\"#\">webform at the bottom of this page</a> to make an appointment. You will receive a confirmation email shortly.\r\n\r\nIf you have additional questions, need to cancel your appointment, or the webform doesn\'t work for you, please email <a href=\"mailto:auditions@theatreatfirst.org\">auditions@theatreatfirst.org</a>.'),
