	(584,90,'description_of_show','What would you do if you suddenly found yourself living in the world of Hamlet? When Rosencrantz &amp; Guildenstern find themselves rushing toward Elsinore with the rules of probability playing funny tricks, they don\'t know which way is up! Celebrate T@F\'s 10th Anniversary with Tom Stoppard\'s wise and witty masterwork.'),
